Chiaki who is in the world beyond...

388
00:14:14,487 --> 00:14:15,821
Grandma!

389
00:14:15,822 --> 00:14:17,989
Chiaki...?

390
00:14:17,990 --> 00:14:22,394
She's my mother who died in a traffic
accident 4 years ago.

392
00:14:23,196 --> 00:14:25,097
Chiaki always warn him about

393
00:14:25,098 --> 00:14:27,699
using the electric shaver
when taking a bath saying,

395
00:14:27,700 --> 00:14:30,969
Don't use it with the cord on
because it's dangerous.

397
00:14:30,970 --> 00:14:33,805
And you, Yoko?

398
00:14:33,806 --> 00:14:36,708
I'm his second wife and married him
two years ago.

400
00:14:36,709 --> 00:14:38,977
I used to be in the same class
as Chiaki in nurse school,

402
00:14:38,978 --> 00:14:41,446
and she used to complain to me a lot.

403
00:14:42,782 --> 00:14:44,483
Inspector, please watch!

404
00:14:44,951 --> 00:14:47,686
He tries to shave using this mirror,

405
00:14:47,687 --> 00:14:50,355
the part where the shaver is
plugged into the extension cord

407
00:14:50,356 --> 00:14:52,390
stops on the edge of the tub.

408
00:14:52,391 --> 00:14:54,893
Very dangerous indeed.

409
00:14:54,894 --> 00:14:57,462
Where were you all during a black out?

410
00:14:57,463 --> 00:15:00,198
We were all in the kitchen.

411
00:15:00,199 --> 00:15:06,304
I saw mother go up the stairs by the
corridor opposite the bathroom too.

413
00:15:06,305 --> 00:15:07,873
If so, then the only likely conclusion
would be that...

415
00:15:07,874 --> 00:15:13,945
Mr. Araide mistakenly pulled the cord
of the shaver into the water

417
00:15:13,946 --> 00:15:16,548
while he was shaving, and electrocuted.

418
00:15:16,549 --> 00:15:18,617
This is an accidental death.

419
00:15:18,618 --> 00:15:20,018
I guess so...

420
00:15:25,258 --> 00:15:28,426
Hey!! Cut out that mischief!

421
00:15:28,427 --> 00:15:31,429
But, my head is messed up and feel like
falling down.

423
00:15:31,430 --> 00:15:33,031
Huh? Why?

424
00:15:33,032 --> 00:15:35,901
Well, the man who died
was shaving standing up,

426
00:15:35,902 --> 00:15:39,304
and Detective Takagi
was copying him, right?

428
00:15:39,305 --> 00:15:41,373
If so, when he got electric shock,

429
00:15:41,374 --> 00:15:45,310
his head is supposed to come
this way like Detective Takagi, right?

431
00:15:45,311 --> 00:15:50,115
But, that man's head was
faced the other way. I wonder why?

433
00:15:50,116 --> 00:15:51,416
That's true.

434
00:15:51,417 --> 00:15:53,585
Hey, this may probably be...

435
00:15:54,720 --> 00:15:56,755
Phooey! No big deal!

436
00:16:00,593 --> 00:16:03,461
While Mr. Araide was shaving...

437
00:16:03,462 --> 00:16:06,665
he realized that the cord was going to
fall into the water...

439
00:16:06,666 --> 00:16:08,700
and rushed to pick it up...

440
00:16:08,701 --> 00:16:11,436
but he pulled it into the tub instead.

441
00:16:11,437 --> 00:16:18,810
He then touched the railing
accidentally and was electrocuted.

443
00:16:18,811 --> 00:16:20,378
So, you see!

444
00:16:21,414 --> 00:16:24,516
Hmm...pretty good, Pops.

445
00:16:24,851 --> 00:16:30,622
Agh! No! Don't touch that! The razor is
vital proof, isn't it?

447
00:16:30,623 --> 00:16:34,059
Touch it? I'm just holding it!

448
00:16:34,060 --> 00:16:35,760
How about you, Detective Takagi?

449
00:16:35,761 --> 00:16:38,563
No, I only held it in my hand too...?

450
00:16:38,564 --> 00:16:40,599
How about the Investigation officer?

451
00:16:40,600 --> 00:16:43,268
I just took pictures.

452
00:16:43,269 --> 00:16:47,339
Strange. Then I wonder who played such
a bad prank like this...?

454
00:16:47,340 --> 00:16:50,141
Just what are you trying to get at?!

455
00:16:50,676 --> 00:16:54,880
Because look, the switch of the razor is
turned off!!

457
00:16:55,481 --> 00:16:57,983
What's going on?

458
00:16:57,984 --> 00:16:59,818
It is strange after all!!

459
00:16:59,819 --> 00:17:03,121
If he was electrocuted while shaving
the switch would have to be on...

461
00:17:03,122 --> 00:17:09,160
The switch must've moved when you fell

462
00:17:09,161 --> 00:17:10,562
Iike so...

463
00:17:12,732 --> 00:17:16,835
Huh? The plug should've been pulled out
to avoid danger.

465
00:17:16,836 --> 00:17:19,070
Yes, I have it right here!

466
00:17:19,071 --> 00:17:22,073
I see! This is the battery charge type!

467
00:17:23,943 --> 00:17:25,777
Then, why was it switched off?

468
00:17:25,778 --> 00:17:29,147
I wasn't moving when
the body was found, was it?

470
00:17:30,650 --> 00:17:32,851
I think...that's only natural.

471
00:17:33,452 --> 00:17:36,588
Somebody didnlt want the noise of the
shaver to be heard!

473
00:17:36,589 --> 00:17:39,758
Huh? Who didn't want it to be heard
by who?

475
00:17:39,759 --> 00:17:44,529
Beats me! I'm just making guesses!

476
00:17:45,898 --> 00:17:46,964
Maybe,

477
00:17:46,965 --> 00:17:52,804
someone could put the cord into
the tub without Mr. Araide noticing?

479
00:17:52,872 --> 00:17:54,072
You idiot! He'd inotice* *

480
00:17:54,073 --> 00:17:58,243
If you did something like that, even if
the shaver wasn't making any noise!

482
00:17:58,411 --> 00:18:02,781
Besides, everyone has an alibi when the
the house blacked out...

484
00:18:02,915 --> 00:18:07,719
When the lights went on, it turned off
once then went on again, right?

486
00:18:10,189 --> 00:18:14,426
Hikaru? You were the one who went to
Iift the breaker, weren't you?

488
00:18:14,427 --> 00:18:15,493
Yes!!

489
00:18:15,494 --> 00:18:19,998
Did you lift the breaker twice back then?

490
00:18:19,999 --> 00:18:25,136
Oh, I'm sorry!! I seem to have touched the
wrong switch,

492
00:18:25,137 --> 00:18:27,472
The breaker of another place
seems to have been lowered,

494
00:18:27,473 --> 00:18:30,241
so I put it back again right away...

495
00:18:30,242 --> 00:18:33,111
I'm really sorry!!

496
00:18:33,112 --> 00:18:39,483
Inspector, the second one was the
overload current breaker...Maybe this is...

498
00:18:40,252 --> 00:18:43,454
Maybe a timer was rigged so that there
would be a black out,

500
00:18:43,455 --> 00:18:49,260
and if someone went into the bathroom
to sneak the electric cord into the tub,

502
00:18:49,261 --> 00:18:51,129
anyone of those four could've done so...

503
00:18:51,130 --> 00:18:53,231
It's possible...

504
00:18:53,232 --> 00:18:55,800
Uh, what are you whispering about...?

505
00:18:55,801 --> 00:18:56,868
Oh, no, it's nothing.

506
00:18:56,869 --> 00:19:01,839
I would like to confirm your alibis before
the black out occurred, just in case.

508
00:19:01,840 --> 00:19:04,476
We just gave you our alibis a while ago?!

509
00:19:04,477 --> 00:19:08,880
Huh? Are you saying that
the killer is among us?

511
00:19:08,881 --> 00:19:11,916
Like I just said I'm doing so, just in case!

512
00:19:13,986 --> 00:19:16,021
Oh, you were on the phone all through
the black out?

514
00:19:16,489 --> 00:19:19,758
Yes...from the time before the black out
till the lights went back on.

516
00:19:19,759 --> 00:19:24,762
I was on the phone
by the kitchen entrance.

518
00:19:24,763 --> 00:19:30,802
I was talking to my friend, Masae about
arrangements on the reunion.

520
00:19:30,803 --> 00:19:33,304
Oh, I did receive a catch phone, though

521
00:19:33,305 --> 00:19:37,208
No one answered when I picked it up,
and the person hung up right away...

523
00:19:37,243 --> 00:19:38,943
Detective Takagi, will you verify this
right away!

525
00:19:38,944 --> 00:19:40,045
Yes, sir!

526
00:19:40,713 --> 00:19:45,884
Was looking for a flashlight when it
blacked out and handed it over to Hikaru.

528
00:19:45,885 --> 00:19:48,253
I was here in the kitchen right through...

529
00:19:48,254 --> 00:19:50,722
Can someone verify that for you?

531
00:19:50,723 --> 00:19:53,024
No not really

532
00:19:53,025 --> 00:19:55,727
Tomoaki was here all the while.

533
00:19:56,829 --> 00:19:59,697
After Hikaru went to raise the breaker,

534
00:19:59,698 --> 00:20:03,601
I was scared, so I was clinging on to
Tomoaki until the lights went on!

536
00:20:03,836 --> 00:20:05,470
Are you sure?

537
00:20:07,339 --> 00:20:08,373
Why?

538
00:20:09,375 --> 00:20:13,878
So like I said, I thought he was my dad.

539
00:20:14,346 --> 00:20:17,015
Next, Mitsu, where were you?

540
00:20:17,016 --> 00:20:22,754
I had just finished climbing the stairs
when the lights went out.

542
00:20:22,755 --> 00:20:26,624
And, I fingered my way to
my room upstairs.

544
00:20:26,625 --> 00:20:33,031
But, I hear that when the lights went back
on, you were downstairs near the kitchen

546
00:20:33,032 --> 00:20:35,834
I felt a presence.

547
00:20:35,835 --> 00:20:39,838
Just as I was about to hit the sack,
I felt a presence outside my room...

549
00:20:39,839 --> 00:20:41,439
Don't tell me...

550
00:20:41,440 --> 00:20:44,409
Someone else other than all of you
had snuck into the house?!

552
00:20:44,410 --> 00:20:50,348
I felt that way and*followed the
sound downstairs. But, I found out.

554
00:20:50,349 --> 00:20:51,716
What did you find out?

555
00:20:51,717 --> 00:20:53,885
It was the sound of the rain.

556
00:20:57,455 --> 00:20:59,891
And, finally you, Hikaru.

557
00:20:59,892 --> 00:21:01,559
Yes!

558
00:21:01,560 --> 00:21:07,031
I went over to the breaker to turn on
the lights...I'm still not used to this house,

560
00:21:07,066 --> 00:21:09,601
so I got lost a bit, though...

561
00:21:09,602 --> 00:21:12,871
You didn't notice anyone suspicious,
did you?

563
00:21:12,872 --> 00:21:14,739
No nobody...

564
00:21:19,111 --> 00:21:20,411
Just as I thought.

565
00:21:20,412 --> 00:21:24,682
I noticed you were
holding your arm...

567
00:21:24,683 --> 00:21:27,852
You're always much too tolerant
from before.

569
00:21:27,853 --> 00:21:29,454
A burn?

570
00:21:29,455 --> 00:21:30,755
Excuse me,

571
00:21:30,756 --> 00:21:34,726
but I'd like to treat her wound
so would it be all right to go to the clinic?

573
00:21:34,727 --> 00:21:38,363
Yes, but please have the officer in the
corridor accompany you!

575
00:21:38,364 --> 00:21:40,632
We'reiunder surveillance, eh?

576
00:21:41,834 --> 00:21:43,868
Oh, and one more thing!

577
00:21:43,869 --> 00:21:49,908
You seem to be the only one who had left
the house between Spm and 7pm

579
00:21:49,909 --> 00:21:51,543
where were you?

580
00:21:51,544 --> 00:21:54,312
I went as-temporary basket ball coach for
alhigh school basket ball club!

582
00:21:54,313 --> 00:22:00,051
It's my alma mater, and since my mentor
broke his bone,

584
00:22:00,052 --> 00:22:02,587
I'm substituting for him until he recovers.

585
00:22:02,588 --> 00:22:05,890
You, a doctor, a basketball coach?

586
00:22:05,891 --> 00:22:08,693
You can go ahead and ask Ran about it.

587
00:22:09,461 --> 00:22:13,765
I go to coach for Teitan High School, the
school that Ran goes to

589
00:22:15,201 --> 00:22:18,435
You know, the advisor of the basketball
club Mr. Tabuchi, don't you?

591
00:22:18,436 --> 00:22:19,637
Oh, yes.

592
00:22:20,205 --> 00:22:26,310
Hey, don't tell me that the reason for
karate club that Ran was going to daily is...

594
00:22:28,047 --> 00:22:32,584
It can't be?!

