00:24:08,681 --> 00:24:09,847
Okay!

640
00:24:11,317 --> 00:24:13,951
I wonder why the lights went out?

641
00:24:13,952 --> 00:24:16,287
Come to think of it, that man was saying

642
00:24:16,288 --> 00:24:19,524
something about experimenting while
